= Next Steps

The `gate_server` is now at a pause, and a server capable of accepting `TCP` client connections and conducting high-concurrency communication is basically complete. Next, we will continue to implement message protocol-related content, introduce the `Protobuf` message library, and carry out message distribution, further improving the gateway server functionality. This part will be revisited after implementing the scene server `scene_server` in the next step, so stay tuned!
